   ░ ██                                                                  ██ ░
   ░ ██     A girl mysteriously disappears on a yachting trip. While     ██ ░
   ░ ██     her lover and her best  friend  search  for  her  across     ██ ░
   ░ ██     Italy, they begin  an  affair.  Antonioni's  penetrating     ██ ░
   ░ ██     study of the idle upper  class  offers  stinging  obser-     ██ ░
   ░ ██     vations on spiritual isolation and the many meanings  of     ██ ░
   ░ ██     love. This is truly a milestone of film grammar.             ██ ░
